briefTitle: Study on Breast Cancer Patient Perspectives of Exercise
officialTitle: Study on Breast Cancer Patient Perspectives of Exercise
primaryOutcomeMeasure: Number of subjects providing completed surveys
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* women,
* breast cancer diagnosis,
* all races will be included.

Exclusion Criteria:

* men,
* those with no breast cancer (ductal carcinoma in situ),
* pregnant women,
* children
